  <description type="morphology">Bulbs narrowly ovoid, 25–60 mm, sometimes producing sessile offsets. Leaves 12–25 cm; blade distinctly mottled with irregular streaks of brown or white, ovate to broadly lanceolate, margins wavy. Scape ± reddish, 15–40 cm. Inflorescences 1–3-flowered. Flowers: tepals white to creamy white with yellow base at anthesis, sometimes pinkish in age, sometimes with red lines or bands, elliptic to narrowly ovate, 25–40 mm, inner with small auricles at base; stamens 12–25 mm; filaments white, flattened, ± lanceolate, 2–3 mm wide; anthers cream to yellow; style white, 12–18 mm; stigma with recurved lobes 3–6 mm. Capsules oblong to narrowly obovoid, 3–5 cm. 2n = 24.</description>
